1. leave my house and go to the 29th skytrain station
2. wait for the skytrain

  while the skytrain is not comming if the upcomming skytrain is not 29th station (while)
    - wait for the skytrain

3. get on the skytrain
4. wait for 4 stops to Granville skytrain station

  until the skytrain has still to do 4 stops (for)
    - stay on the skytrain

5. got off the skystrain
6. walk to ITD and enter the school if open

  if ITD is open (if)
    - enter the school
  else
    - go back home
    
